@NODE It_works_on_my_machine..._8-) "It works on my machine... 8-)"
TRW is tested as much as I can given my resources at hand.
Still, there may be a nasty bug or two within it, especially
during the development process.  The end user is urged to make
full @{" backups " Link backups} before using this utility. To do otherwise would be
folly.  Be warned, as I will not be held responsible for any
damage to your BBS. Until it proves itself, you are always well
advised to be paranoid about software of this nature.

@ENDNODE

